{"tid":2442006,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蒸發2萬億 微博禁搜「股市」","createTime":"2021-03-11T05:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T05:41:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"80e1af3d8d1f2de8566b3edcf6d7a1a462ba7d69","tid":2442006,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210311/R3KDI7SKWNCSFGACUAYRMJMCZE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210311%2FR3KDI7SKWNCSFGACUAYRMJMCZE%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHZ6X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=925c1f8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210311%2FR3KDI7SKWNCSFGACUAYRMJMCZE%2F&h=28e376e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210311/R3KDI7SKWNCSFGACUAYRMJMCZE/</a><br />\n<br />\n蒸發2萬億 微博禁搜「股市」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nP6KC9uxUapHp0ks7gdV0wWfs6Y=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YHJENC5AYVHCNAFHFM6FUTAAVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnP6KC9uxUapHp0ks7gdV0wWfs6Y%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYHJENC5AYVHCNAFHFM6FUTAAVQ.jpg&h=c061feac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球股市波動撞正兩會舉行，中國股市連日大跌，試過一日蒸發2萬億人民幣（2.4萬億港元）。前日更傳「國家隊」入市護盤，但無阻跌勢，微博昨直接將「股市」及「股市暴跌」列為敏感詞，收市前搜索兩詞不時無法顯示結果。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：表決修改草案 可向副總理開刀  《組織法》左右二十大佈局<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「國家隊」進場難阻跌勢<br />\n<br />\n彭博日前引述消息指，避免兩會期間股市繼續探底，中國政府已命令股市國家隊於9日進場護盤。可惜中國股市仍然跌不停，上證綜合指數由3月4日至9日收市，累跌6.1%，從今年2月19日的高點來看，更下跌9.1%。<br />\n<br />\n股市暴跌，中共則試圖控制輿論。昨日多個中國大型財經新聞頭版都沒有特別提到A股暴跌，微博更將「股市」及「股市暴跌」列為敏感詞，「股票」、「A股」和「暴跌」等關鍵字則沒有受影響。本報記者到微博搜索「股市」及「股市暴跌」，在昨天收市前大部份時間無法搜索，但收市後卻能夠看到搜查結果。經中央出手干預，昨日股市終。。。。<br />\n。。。。<br />\n<br />\n彭博／《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"c5e869a40c8a519c0b05159d1d6543ce8e0dd4d4","tid":2442006,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:41:52.000Z","msg":"今日推番上去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}